      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residual norms and energy balance monitored; iterative solver convergence confirmed.",
      "rationale": "Force and displacement residuals converged to below 1e-4 relative tolerance in all load steps. Energy balance errors remained below 0.1% throughout the simulation."
