      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup and boundary condition application by a second analyst.",
      "rationale": "A second qualified FEA engineer independently reviewed the model setup, boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions. No discrepancies were identified that would affect the quantities of interest."
