      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum mechanics assumptions and contact formulation justified relative to physical behavior of metallic implant under quasi-static bending.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model for titanium alloy screw and rod is appropriate for the sub-yield loading regime of F1717. Frictionless contact at screw-rod interface is justified by lubrication present during testing. Model form is consistent with prior published FDA validation studies."
