      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of loading scenarios relevant to the intended use.",
      "rationale": "Testing was performed at a single offset distance (35 mm) per ASTM F1717. This represents only one of several clinically relevant loading configurations. The shortfall in this factor is acknowledged; overall credibility remains sufficient given the regulatory context of ASTM F1717 as a standardized acceptance test."
